{"tid":1023143,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］有無人個牙較會痛？","createTime":"2019-02-15T14:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T14:46:10.000Z","uid":90300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac0ff8c96f1c1105c7845ad71b4a4a24d9a6fcf","tid":1023143,"uid":90300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:07:14.000Z","msg":"中學開始牙較食野會痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尤其係講得太多野或者牙較郁動太多之後 <br />\n例如唱K 游水（用口呼吸要開合開合）<br />\n有時嚴重會個開唔大個口 好似個牙較緊左實左咁<br />\n同埋開合會卡卡聲 勁驚會甩較<br />\n同埋淨係右邊牙較會痛 久而久之咬唔到好硬同煙韌既野<br />\n持續左差唔多十年 睇過幾次醫生 牙醫 脊醫 啪骨正骨<br />\n懷疑過關唔關隻智慧齒事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都係得唔到解答 次次都係開消炎止痛藥 <br />\n過一兩星期又翻發<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人可以解答到我 至少知道可以去邊睇醫生"},{"pid":"d1076a6fb6dffa1715da1a8293cd40dc9e1918ac","tid":1023143,"uid":90300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:09:03.000Z","msg":"推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7aace593978899aaa02011068a8b5f3ca67b20","tid":1023143,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:11:48.000Z","msg":"照X光<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1718076b6a4d3184a074373e9735b8925281682b","tid":1023143,"uid":90300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d7aace593978899aaa02011068a8b5f3ca67b20","tid":1023143,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:11:48.000Z","msg":"照X光<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:13:49.000Z","msg":"牙醫果度照過 但都無咩結論<br />\n都唔知去邊科度照"},{"pid":"a5dc4349d7abca076b524fe930863b89ec316719","tid":1023143,"uid":235520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:30:27.000Z","msg":"牙胶病無得醫架（有既 做手術 但一般情況下醫生唔會建議 因為風險都高）<br />\n<br />\n有冇食香口膠習慣？ <br />\n我估你有埋夜晚磨牙習慣？"},{"pid":"da6d3c63ed8b5d60cd534570d